MID_X015_ED1: $t1$Wmマークス|3$Wmジークベルト|7$w0|$Wsマークス|$Wa$E怒,汗|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_EVT_04|Siegbert... It wasn't reported to me\nthat enemies would just appear like that.$k$pWhy did you stay silent until now?$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E怒,汗|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_EVT_06|I...\nI didn't want to disappoint Father.$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E通常,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_MYROOM_10|What do you mean?$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E苦,汗|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_DAMAGE_00|The people looking after me, and everyone\nelse had said how strong Father was...$k$pThat he has great character...$k$pBecause I'm your son, in order to\nbecome a splended person, like you...$k$pI felt that I needed to defeat\nthat many enemies by myself...$k$pThat's why I never mentioned it...$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E苦,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_EVT_14|...I see.\nSo that's why...$k$pIn the time I was gone... you\nhave endured this all by yourself.$k$p…………$k$p$E笑,|...You really are splendid, Siegbert.$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E怒,汗|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_EVT_00|Father...? But I haven't done\nanything to deserve your praise...$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$SvpVOICE_MARKS_B_WIN_02|Yes, you have. You fought\nto the end... all by yourself.$k$pIf I didn't recognize that,\nI'd be a terrible father.$k$pYou've put in plenty of effort.\nThere's nothing to be ashamed of.$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E通常,|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_DAMAGE_01|!!$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E苦,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_EVT_20|I'm sorry... All this time, I've caused\nproblems for you without realizing it.$k$pFrom now on, let there be no secrets\nbetween us. Let's talk about many things.$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa…………$k$p$E怒,|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_EVT_01|Father...$k$pIf that's the case, will you...\nAllow me to go with you?$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E通常,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_MYROOM_02|...What?$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E苦,汗|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_EVT_07|Well... I know that you're worried for me,\nand you don't want me to be in the war.$k$pBut, I don't like it. I want to leave\nhere, and be helpful to Father!$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa…………$k$p$E怒,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_EVT_00|Are you sure?\nReal war is relentless.$k$pIf you have anything to cry about,\nI'll bring you back immediately.$k$pIs that still okay?$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E怒,|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_EVT_04|Yes.\nI promise I won't hinder you.$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$E笑,|$SvpVOICE_MARKS_EVT_11|...I see.$k$pThen, from now on, you're our ally.\nLet me welcome you, Siegbert.$k\n$Wsジークベルト|$Wa$E笑,|$SvpVOICE_SIEGBERT_MYROOM_10|Thank you...!$k\n$Wsマークス|$Wa$SvpVOICE_MARKS_B_SUPPORT_03|Let's fight together.$k$pI won't leave you with\nany more painful feelings...$k$pAs your father, I vow to protect you.$k
